metadata.description: HIDDEN ONES are 10,151 Cryptids lurking in the forests of the Metaverse. Cryptids grant membership to an exclusive community building the Hidden Lakes Cinematic Universe: a decentralized, crypto-native film franchise! Inspired by the “HIDDEN MAN”, the creature from the genesis movie “He Who Lives In Hidden Lakes”, each Cryptid is a hand-drawn & unique NFT with members-only access to events, giveaways, NFT claims, workshops, IP usage, and more.
